  "name": "RPlog_Confrontation_with_Morganna",
  "title": "Confrontation with Morganna",
  "summary": "Descending into the Twi'lek sector of Nar Shaddaa, the Jedi Jessalyn (Annalar) and her apprentice, the mechanic Fritz-Orson, sense a familiar Dark presence and come face to face with the feral Sith Morganna, shopping for silver claws. Recognizing one another, the confrontation erupts into a duel: Morganna assaults Orson's mind and throat with the dark side and hurls a fireball at Jessalyn, who absorbs it at the cost of a badly burned hand. Orson, retreating into a deeper inner reality, throws off Morganna's grip and ignites his lightsaber, fighting with surprising strength and certainty alongside Jessalyn. Outmatched by his powerful mind and pressed between two Jedi, Morganna flings a Twi'lek bystander as a distraction and melts into the crowd to plan anew. Shaken but victorious, the wounded pair tend to each other, share their love, and flee toward their ship, knowing their vacation, and their secrecy, is over.",
